{
  "an1.198-208:1.0.1": "\"Etadaggaṁ, bhikkhave, mama sāvakānaṁ bhikkhūnaṁ manomayaṁ kāyaṁ abhinimminantānaṁ yadidaṁ cūḷapanthako.(1)",
  "an1.198-208:1.0.2": "…   Cetovivaṭṭakusalānaṁ yadidaṁ cūḷapanthako.(2)",
  "an1.198-208:1.0.3": "…   Saññāvivaṭṭakusalānaṁ yadidaṁ mahāpanthako.(3)",
  "an1.198-208:1.0.4": "…   Araṇavihārīnaṁ yadidaṁ subhūti.(4)",
  "an1.198-208:1.0.5": "…   Dakkhiṇeyyānaṁ yadidaṁ subhūti.(5)",
  "an1.198-208:1.0.6": "…   Āraññakānaṁ yadidaṁ revato khadiravaniyo.(6)",
  "an1.198-208:1.0.7": "…   Jhāyīnaṁ yadidaṁ kaṅkhārevato.(7)",
  "an1.198-208:1.0.8": "…   Āraddhavīriyānaṁ yadidaṁ soṇo koḷiviso.(8)",
  "an1.198-208:1.0.9": "…   Kalyāṇavākkaraṇānaṁ yadidaṁ soṇo kuṭikaṇṇo.(9)"
}